---
title: Smokey Pork Tacos with Charred Pineapple & Cucumber Salsa
description: Dinner is all about balance. Just like how the sweet pineapple salsa balances the smokey spice blend on these morsels of pan-fried pork. Now the only tricky thing is balancing all the ingredients in your very full tacos as you try to eat them - don't worry, it's worth it!
